text: Cairo Station also called The Iron Gate ( Bāb al-Ḥadīd) is a 1958 Egyptian crime drama movie directed by Youssef Chahine (who also stars) and also starring Fariq Shawqi, Hind Rostom, Said Khalil. ==Other websites== * * Category:1958 crime movies Category:1958 drama movies Category:1950s crime drama movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies directed by Youssef Chahine
title: Cairo Station
